Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.07,0:00:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮诺  男人只要抓住了他的胃袋就万事OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要像挖坑一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖坑一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.50,0:23:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把拳头捅进去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.11,0:23:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捅进去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.95,0:23:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  第6桥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第6桥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错  刚才你确实抓住胃袋了
